        <para>kdelibs5 (KDE4 core libraries and binaries for all KDE4 applications)</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>libkjsembed1  (Embedded JavaScript library)
              (for the the optional Javascripting function in Krusader)</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2>

