      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>kdelibs5-dev (installs many development libraries for KDE4)</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>libphonon-dev (libphonon-dev cross-platform multimedia framework development)</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2>



